---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Nick Sammons | North Georgia REALTOR®">
	<main class="relative z-0">
		<!-- Introduction -->
		<section class="py-16 md:py-32 px-6 lg:px-12 max-w-7xl mx-auto">
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 md:gap-20 items-center">
				<div class="relative">
					<img 
						src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/nick-headshot.jpg" 
						alt="Nick Sammons" 
						class="w-full h-[400px] md:h-[700px] object-cover grayscale shadow-2xl"
					/>
					<div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 hidden xl:block w-72 h-48 bg-navy-900 p-10 flex flex-col justify-center border-r-4 border-gold-400">
						<p class="text-white text-2xl font-serif italic leading-tight text-center">Your North Georgia Partner.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="space-y-6 md:space-y-10">
					<span class="text-xs font-bold text-gold-500 uppercase tracking-widest">The Realtor</span>
					<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif tracking-tight leading-none">Nick <span class="italic text-stone-500">Sammons.</span></h1>
					<div class="prose prose-stone font-light text-stone-600 leading-relaxed text-base md:text-lg space-y-4 md:space-y-6">
						<p>
							Nick Sammons is a professional REALTOR® based right here in Georgia. Born and raised in Gwinnett County, he moved to North Georgia after high school and has called it home ever since. Building on early experience in sales, he has become a standout leader in real estate.
						</p>
						<p>
							Known for his resourcefulness, discipline, and no-nonsense approach, Nick goes the extra mile every time to deliver exceptional service. He is committed to transparency, open communication, and truly listening to clients, whether it's crafting the story of their dream home or navigating a tough market.
						</p>
						<p>
							From buying and selling to rentals and investment properties, Nick handles it all with dedication and a focus on client satisfaction. Outside of real estate, Nick is an avid golfer and an ISSA Certified Personal Trainer and Nutritionist, passionate about helping others get stronger and feel their best.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Philosophy / Experience Section -->
		<section class="py-24 md:py-48 px-6 lg:px-12 bg-white overflow-hidden border-y border-stone-100">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
				<div class="space-y-12">
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<span class="text-xs font-bold text-gold-500 uppercase tracking-widest">Our Approach</span>
						<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif tracking-tight leading-none">Elevated <span class="italic text-stone-500">Service.</span></h2>
					</div>
					<div class="prose prose-stone prose-lg text-stone-600 font-light max-w-xl">
						<p>Real estate is more than a transaction; it's the foundation of your next chapter. We combine the latest industry technology with a high-touch, personalized approach to ensure every client feels guided, informed, and confident.</p>
						<p>From strategic marketing for sellers to exhaustive market research for buyers, our commitment to excellence is reflected in every detail of our work.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-12 pt-8 border-t border-stone-100">
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 text-navy-900">Modern Strategy</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-stone-500">Leveraging data-driven insights to maximize property value and reach.</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-2 text-navy-900">Brand Integrity</h4>
							<p class="text-sm text-stone-500">A commitment to professionalism that honors the Chris McCall Realty legacy.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Mosaic Group -->
				<div class="relative">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-12 gap-4 h-[600px] md:h-[800px]">
						<div class="col-span-8 row-span-7 relative group overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
							<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/listings/7115-shady-oak.jpg" alt="Luxury Home" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" />
						</div>
						<div class="col-span-4 row-span-5 col-start-9 row-start-2 relative group overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
							<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/listings/dsc-6393.jpg" alt="Detail" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" />
						</div>
						<div class="col-span-5 row-span-4 col-start-2 row-start-8 relative group overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
							<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/listings/dsc-6370.jpg" alt="Detail" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" />
						</div>
						<div class="col-span-5 row-span-5 col-start-7 row-start-8 relative group overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
							<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/listings/beechwood-master.jpg" alt="Interior" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700" />
						</div>
					</div>
					<!-- Gold Accent -->
					<div class="absolute -bottom-10 -right-10 w-40 h-40 bg-gold-400/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -z-10"></div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Mccall Properties Info -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-16 md:py-32 px-6 lg:px-12 border-t border-gold-400/20">
			<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8 md:space-y-12">
				<img src="/NickSammonsReality/assets/mccall-logo-final.png" alt="Chris McCall Realtor" class="h-12 md:h-16 w-auto mx-auto" />
				<h2 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-serif tracking-tight text-white">Representing <span class="italic text-gold-400">Chris McCall Realtor</span></h2>
				<p class="text-stone-400 text-base md:text-lg font-light leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
					Operating under the prestigious Chris McCall Realtor banner, Nick leverages a robust network and decades of regional expertise. Chris McCall Realtor is known for its deep roots in the North Georgia community and its commitment to high-integrity property transactions across residential, commercial, and investment sectors.
				</p>
				<div class="pt-10">
					<a href="/NickSammonsReality/contact" class="inline-block px-12 py-5 border border-gold-400/30 hover:bg-gold-400 hover:text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest transition-all shadow-xl">
						Partner With Us
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
